                     <layoutDesc>
                        <layout columns="1" writtenLines="10">
                           <p>The inscribed surface is smoothed and is flaked off in several places,
                              especially in the lower part. Traces of red and yellow paint in lines
                              1-6. Round script with squared omicron and sigma. The letters are
                              small, rather symmetrical and well cut, but with a descending
